## Extending Existing Pages

### Page Blocks (inject into existing detail pages)

```tsx
pageBlocks: [
    {
        id: 'my-custom-block',
        title: 'My Custom Section',
        location: {
            pageId: 'channel-detail',  // Target page
            column: 'main',           // 'main' or 'side'
            position: {
                blockId: 'channel-defaults',  // Anchor block
                order: 'after',              // 'before' or 'after'
            },
        },
        component: ({ context }) => {
            const entityId = context.entity?.id;
            // Render custom UI
        },
    },
],
```

### Action Bar Items (add buttons to existing pages)

```tsx
actionBarItems: [
    {
        pageId: 'order-detail',
        component: ({ context }) => {
            const order = context.entity;
            return (
                <Button onClick={() => handleAction(order)}>
                    My Action
                </Button>
            );
        },
    },
],
```

