## Checklist for New Dashboard Extension

- [ ] `dashboard/index.tsx` created with `defineDashboardExtension()`
- [ ] GraphQL operations defined in `<entity>.graphql.ts` with fragment
- [ ] List page created with `<ListPage>` component
- [ ] Detail page created with `useDetailPage` hook
- [ ] Create and update modes handled via `params.id === 'new'`
- [ ] Translatable fields use `TranslatableFormFieldWrapper`
- [ ] Non-translatable fields use `FormFieldWrapper`
- [ ] `requiresPermission` set on `navMenuItem` in list page route
- [ ] `<PermissionGuard>` wrapping submit button in detail page
- [ ] `requiresPermission` set on `DataTableBulkActionItem` in bulk actions
- [ ] Toast notifications on success/error
- [ ] Bulk actions registered (at minimum: delete)
- [ ] `dashboard: './dashboard/index.tsx'` added to `@VendurePlugin` decorator
- [ ] Navigation menu item configured with correct `sectionId`
- [ ] Hidden columns configured in `defaultVisibility` (id, languageCode, translations)
- [ ] Tables use `ListPage`, `DataTable`, or `Table` primitives from `@vendure/dashboard` (no raw HTML tables)

